name: Neco-Arc (Mittelflagge)
description:
Neco-Arc is a Neco Spirit appearing in the Tsukihime visual novel series. She is a pint-size cat girl parody of Arcueid Brunestud, acting as the mascot character of Type-Moon.

Made by the "amiguitos toxicos" discord community.

There's TWO of them Can be found on Nordflagge and Germany Flag / Extension of the Middle.
